data.description: $5,000 BUYER INCENTIVE!! Call a Realtor for all the details. Do you love to entertain? This dwelling has space for entertaining inside & out. Conveniently located in North Fort Payne offering 3 (or 4) bedrooms, 2 baths and so much more. Freshly painted interior helps accent the beautiful hardwood & tile floors. Updated light fixtures and NEW kitchen appliances. Vaulted ceiling living room w/gas log FP. Large Den/Family room w/gas log FP and lots of natural light. Additional finished room w/skylights offers a 4th BR or home gym/playroom/home office. Enclosed sunporch adjacent to the oversized screen porch that leads to an open deck and fenced back yard. Basement workshop w/roll-up door.
